				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/C%E1%BB%95-b%C3%A1ch-h%C3%A0nh/poem-_Rd3Exuz3Fn9VBE_R4m_tQ">Cổ bách hành - 古柏行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-Thu%C3%BD-Ki%E1%BB%81u-truy%E1%BB%87n-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-otOLPa1RhgIqnWq_JmtyEg">Độc Thuý Kiều truyện cảm tác - 讀翠翹傳感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/M%E1%BA%ADu-T%C3%BD-nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A1n-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-kb9QHbvpBqcxu6UiONZStQ">Mậu Tý nguyên đán cảm tác - 戊子元旦感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-GfNq85EUzTvOO-A-Y5zO9w">Phan Đình Phùng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-V%C3%B4/%C3%94-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-AyYmTKS7zK8CMxxvsdaI5Q">Ô dạ đề - 烏夜啼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%91ng-V%C3%B4/author-iY30jDgVJV8eG4rWx8K3sw">Tống Vô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/S%E1%BB%9F-Khanh-ho%E1%BA%A1-Ki%E1%BB%81u-t%E1%BA%A1i-Ng%C6%B0ng-B%C3%ADch-l%C3%A2u-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-c%E1%BA%A3m-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-thi/poem-QTKCDgRinybg6F5dLA27cw">Sở Khanh hoạ Kiều tại Ngưng Bích lâu tức cảnh cảm đề thi - 楚卿和翹在凝碧樓即景感題詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/S%C6%A1n-qu%E1%BB%B7/poem--HdoULiVENCa2j4WOpRBSg">Sơn quỷ - 山鬼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://